<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="card shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-body p-5">
      <h1 class="display-5 mb-4 text-center">For Venue Owners</h1>

      <p class="lead text-center mb-4">
        Get your venue on the map and attract live music fans in your area.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-4" />

      <h4>Step 1: Complete Your Profile</h4>
      <p>
        Go to <strong>Edit Profile</strong> from your dashboard to add your venue name, bio, and a profile image. This helps artists and fans know who you are.
      </p>

      <h4>Step 2: Add Your Venue</h4>
      <p>
        From the dashboard, click <strong>"Add Venue"</strong>. Enter your location, type (bar, club, etc.), and description. This will place your venue on the map.
      </p>

      <h4>Step 3: Post an Event</h4>
      <p>
        After creating a venue, click <strong>"Post Event"</strong> to add a live show. Set the date, time, genre, and whether thereâ€™s a cover charge.
      </p>

      <h4>Step 4: Keep Your Listings Current</h4>
      <p>
        Update events as needed. Old shows disappear automatically after the end time.
      </p>

      <hr class="my-5" />

      <div class="text-center">
        <%= link_to "Sign Up as an Owner!", new_owner_registration_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
